Ruler On Ice Wins 143rd Belmont Stakes Ahead of Stay Thirsty

-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 
2011-06-11T22:45:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-11/ruler-on-ice-wins-143rd-belmont-stakes-ahead-of-stay-thirsty.html
Ruler on Ice won the 143d Belmont
Stakes, leaving the gate at 24-1 odds at Belmont Park in Elmont,
 New York .  Stay Thirsty, at 16-1, was second and Brilliant Speed, at
10-1, was third.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  